data.description: Beautiful move in ready home on a large lot with mature shade trees. Relax with family or entertain family in the spacious family room with vaulted ceilings and a traditional brick fireplace. Formal Dining room is great for dinner and holiday parties. Cook to your hearts delight in this kitchen with stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops and a breakfast nook for additional seating. Master suite offers an attached bath and his and her walk in closets. Two guest bedrooms and a guest bath will work great for family or overnight guest. Large kid friendly yard offers a covered patio for cookouts and a fenced yard for the kids to run and play. Call for a showing today.
